item.title: Lake Parties, Food, School, and . . . Michael Jackson!
item.description: Some updates… Alright, I’ve got the basic Nav links up. Sadly, I forgot the Affies and Linkage… links. TT_TT I’ll fix it later (read the last paragraph).
